📨 𝙀𝙢𝙖𝙞𝙡 𝙎𝙚𝙣𝙩 𝙎𝙪𝙘𝙘𝙚𝙨𝙨𝙛𝙪𝙡𝙡𝙮! 📨

Hope you haven’t cleared your inboxes yet, Marketistas! ‘Cause you’ve got mail, courtesy of us!

For those who have valiantly joined the FEU JMA family as members, please do check your provided student and alternate emails for your confirmation letter and links to the respective FEU JMA Members’ Group Chat!

Make sure to keep your notifications turned on all year round as we keep you updated on events, on-campus and off-campus engagements, and other opportunities and perks we’ve got to offer! Welcome to FEU JMA! 💙💛

✨ Applications are still open for those who want to join! ✨

STP Applications: https://bit.ly/2025-2026STP

SCM Applications: https://bit.ly/2025-2026SCM

Membership Applications: https://bit.ly/FEUJMAMEMBERS

Membership Renewal: https://bit.ly/FEUJMARENEWAL

JMA Core: https://bit.ly/FEUJMACORE

Talents Membership: https://bit.ly/FEUJMATALENTS

#SOARsogonWithFEUJMA
#30YearsOneFEUJMA
#AboveAndBeyondFEUJMA

Pubmat by Franchaisca Corral
Caption by John Vincent Grey

message.text:
𝐇𝐨𝐧𝐨𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐄𝐱𝐜𝐞𝐥𝐥𝐞𝐧𝐜𝐞: 𝐂𝐞𝐥𝐞𝐛𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐎𝐮𝐫 𝐆𝐮𝐢𝐝𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐋𝐢𝐠𝐡𝐭𝐬

We are proud to celebrate the remarkable achievements and dedication of our faculty members, who embody genuine excellence in both service and academics. Last 𝗦𝗲𝗽𝘁𝗲𝗺𝗯𝗲𝗿 𝟱, 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱, we honored them through 𝙃𝙤𝙣𝙤𝙧𝙞𝙣𝙜 𝙩𝙝𝙚 𝙏𝙖𝙢𝙖𝙧𝙖𝙬 𝘾𝙤𝙢𝙢𝙞𝙩𝙢𝙚𝙣𝙩: 𝘼 𝘾𝙚𝙡𝙚𝙗𝙧𝙖𝙩𝙞𝙤𝙣 𝙤𝙛 𝙎𝙚𝙧𝙫𝙞𝙘𝙚.

Congratulations to our 𝗖𝗮𝗻𝘃𝗮𝘀 𝗖𝗵𝗮𝗺𝗽𝗶𝗼𝗻 and 𝗥𝗲𝘀𝗲𝗮𝗿𝗰𝗵 𝗣𝘂𝗯𝗹𝗶𝗰𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻 𝗔𝘄𝗮𝗿𝗱𝗲𝗲𝘀. Their unwavering pursuit of knowledge and new research not only advances science and healthcare, but also brings pride and honor to our university. Their work inspires colleagues and students to continue pushing the boundaries of innovation.

We also recognize faculty members 𝗰𝗲𝗹𝗲𝗯𝗿𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝟭𝟬 𝗮𝗻𝗱 𝟭𝟱 𝘆𝗲𝗮𝗿𝘀 𝗼𝗳 𝘀𝗲𝗿𝘃𝗶𝗰𝗲 🌟. Their unwavering dedication to teaching, mentoring, and community service exemplifies a legacy of enthusiasm and endurance. For more than a decade, they have guided our MedTech Tams and healthcare professionals, changing lives and leaving an indelible impression on the IHSN community.

#PoweredToBeTimeless
#XIIMTSoc
#FEUMTS

Caption By Maria Victoria Manrique
Publication by Erika Longatang and Rein Dela Cruz

message.text:
𝐇𝐨𝐧𝐨𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐄𝐱𝐜𝐞𝐥𝐥𝐞𝐧𝐜𝐞: 𝐂𝐞𝐥𝐞𝐛𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐎𝐮𝐫 𝐆𝐮𝐢𝐝𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐋𝐢𝐠𝐡𝐭𝐬

We are proud to celebrate the remarkable achievements and dedication of our faculty members, who embody genuine excellence in both service and academics. Last 𝗦𝗲𝗽𝘁𝗲𝗺𝗯𝗲𝗿 𝟱, 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱, we honored them through 𝙃𝙤𝙣𝙤𝙧𝙞𝙣𝙜 𝙩𝙝𝙚 𝙏𝙖𝙢𝙖𝙧𝙖𝙬 𝘾𝙤𝙢𝙢𝙞𝙩𝙢𝙚𝙣𝙩: 𝘼 𝘾𝙚𝙡𝙚𝙗𝙧𝙖𝙩𝙞𝙤𝙣 𝙤𝙛 𝙎𝙚𝙧𝙫𝙞𝙘𝙚.

Congratulations to our 𝗖𝗮𝗻𝘃𝗮𝘀 𝗖𝗵𝗮𝗺𝗽𝗶𝗼𝗻 and 𝗥𝗲𝘀𝗲𝗮𝗿𝗰𝗵 𝗣𝘂𝗯𝗹𝗶𝗰𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻 𝗔𝘄𝗮𝗿𝗱𝗲𝗲𝘀. Their unwavering pursuit of knowledge and new research not only advances science and healthcare, but also brings pride and honor to our university. Their work inspires colleagues and students to continue pushing the boundaries of innovation.

We also recognize faculty members 𝗰𝗲𝗹𝗲𝗯𝗿𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝟭𝟬 𝗮𝗻𝗱 𝟭𝟱 𝘆𝗲𝗮𝗿𝘀 𝗼𝗳 𝘀𝗲𝗿𝘃𝗶𝗰𝗲 🌟. Their unwavering dedication to teaching, mentoring, and community service exemplifies a legacy of enthusiasm and endurance. For more than a decade, they have guided our MedTech Tams and healthcare professionals, changing lives and leaving an indelible impression on the IHSN community.

#PoweredToBeTimeless
#XIIMTSoc
#FEUMTS

Caption By Maria Victoria Manrique
Publication by Erika Longatang and Rein Dela Cruz

message.text:
𝐇𝐨𝐧𝐨𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐄𝐱𝐜𝐞𝐥𝐥𝐞𝐧𝐜𝐞: 𝐂𝐞𝐥𝐞𝐛𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐎𝐮𝐫 𝐆𝐮𝐢𝐝𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐋𝐢𝐠𝐡𝐭𝐬

We are proud to celebrate the remarkable achievements and dedication of our faculty members, who embody genuine excellence in both service and academics. Last 𝗦𝗲𝗽𝘁𝗲𝗺𝗯𝗲𝗿 𝟱, 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱, we honored them through 𝙃𝙤𝙣𝙤𝙧𝙞𝙣𝙜 𝙩𝙝𝙚 𝙏𝙖𝙢𝙖𝙧𝙖𝙬 𝘾𝙤𝙢𝙢𝙞𝙩𝙢𝙚𝙣𝙩: 𝘼 𝘾𝙚𝙡𝙚𝙗𝙧𝙖𝙩𝙞𝙤𝙣 𝙤𝙛 𝙎𝙚𝙧𝙫𝙞𝙘𝙚.

Congratulations to our 𝗖𝗮𝗻𝘃𝗮𝘀 𝗖𝗵𝗮𝗺𝗽𝗶𝗼𝗻 and 𝗥𝗲𝘀𝗲𝗮𝗿𝗰𝗵 𝗣𝘂𝗯𝗹𝗶𝗰𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻 𝗔𝘄𝗮𝗿𝗱𝗲𝗲𝘀. Their unwavering pursuit of knowledge and new research not only advances science and healthcare, but also brings pride and honor to our university. Their work inspires colleagues and students to continue pushing the boundaries of innovation.

We also recognize faculty members 𝗰𝗲𝗹𝗲𝗯𝗿𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝟭𝟬 𝗮𝗻𝗱 𝟭𝟱 𝘆𝗲𝗮𝗿𝘀 𝗼𝗳 𝘀𝗲𝗿𝘃𝗶𝗰𝗲 🌟. Their unwavering dedication to teaching, mentoring, and community service exemplifies a legacy of enthusiasm and endurance. For more than a decade, they have guided our MedTech Tams and healthcare professionals, changing lives and leaving an indelible impression on the IHSN community.

#FEUMTS
